# MHCLG Funding Data Standards

The data standards project came about off the back of a data quality and consistency design sprint that recommended further work be undertaken on Data Standards with the following outputs:

- Define a set of data standards for risk, organisation and finance
- Investigation any existing standards and any gaps to on meeting our user needs
- Define a reusable template for  presenting and consuming data  standards
- Explore technical elements and challenges of implementing data  standards
- Recommendations for implementation, governance and change control
- A further set of recommendations for future data standards.

